# Tachyonot Release Notes

## 3.5.3 (13 September 2024)
This release includes the following new features:
- Support for LLMs on embedded systems with low power requirements such as:
    - No AVX support
    - No GPU support
    - No F16C support
- Support for Intel Atom Goldmont processors
- Migrate from PyInstaller based packaging to Briefcase based packaging
- Minor fixes in NLTK data handling and model weights loading

## 3.5.2 (10 September 2024)
This release includes the following new features:
- Migration from Transformers to LlamaCPP
- Removal of PyTorch and Transformer support there by reducing the disk space usage
- Removal of Llama Index based RAG support and custom RAG support for LLMs introduced

## 1.3.2 (6 August 2024)
This release includes the following new features:
- Reduction in disk space usage py dependencies
- Migration to Transformers from Openvino

* Initial release (24 July 2024)
First official release of Tachyonot. This release includes the following features:
- Support for text based LLMs
- Support for audio based LLMs
- Openvino support for LLMs
- Llama Index based RAG support
- Faiss Based Indexing